The fact that this pin will not pass through this piston, there is a very small, unhappy little edge somewhere.

00:00:41.180 --> 00:00:43.940
This one has already been worked out.

00:00:43.940 --> 00:00:46.220
It just falls through.

00:00:46.220 --> 00:00:50.300
